getInboundTransferRules(address).details: helper to get a list of all of the inbound transfer rules of an account

PERC_BASE.details: used for percUnlockedAtTimeUnlock in transfer rules

transferRulesOutbound.details: each account can have at most 1 outbound transfer rules
